<html lang='en'>

  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>You're Invited to Join UBI as an Agent</title>
    <style>
      .body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 10px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: white;
        color: #2b2b2b;
      }

      .wrapper {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 15px;
      }

      .container {
        background-color: transparent;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #046307;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 8px;
      }

      .email-header h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .email-content {
        padding: 20px;
        color: #2b2b2b;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .email-content h2 {
        margin: 0 0 15px;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #2b2b2b;
      }

      .btn-register {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #046307;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 32px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .btn-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: transparent;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #2b2b2b;
      }

      .email-content a {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .email-footer a {
        color: #0022c9;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class='body'>
    <div class='wrapper'>
      <table class='container'>
        <tr>
          <td class='email-header'>
            <h1>UBI</h1>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class='email-content'>
            <h2>You've Been Invited to Join UBI as an Agent</h2>
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>
              You have been invited by the UBI admin team to register as a field
              agent on the UBI platform. As an agent, you will help verify loan
              applications by conducting field visits and submitting
              verification reports.
            </p>
            <p>Click the button below to complete your registration:</p>

            <div class='btn-wrapper'>
              <a href='{{registrationUrl}}' class='btn-register'>Complete
                Registration</a>
            </div>

            <p>
              This invitation link expires in
              <strong>7 days</strong>. Please register before it expires.
            </p>
            <p>
              If the button above does not work, copy and paste the following
              link into your browser:
              <br />
              <a href='{{registrationUrl}}'>{{registrationUrl}}</a>
            </p>
            <p>
              If you were not expecting this invitation or believe it was sent
              in error, please ignore this email or contact us at
              <a href='mailto:Support@ubi.com'>Support@ubi.com</a>.
            </p>
            <p>Kind Regards,<br />UBI Team</p>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td class='email-footer'>
            If you experience any problems, kindly contact us at
            <a href='mailto:Support@ubi.com'>Support@ubi.com</a>
            or send us a WhatsApp message at
            <strong>+234 813 414 6906</strong>.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>